caption.p: Correlation of F max (left panel) and nonequilibrium work (right panel), W neq, with logBB for the 26 compounds considered in this study ( Table S1) in the case of the CHARMM36 force-field for the DOPC membrane model and pulling velocity v = 0.5 nm/ns ( Table S4). The correlation coefficient R 2 is indicated at the top right corner of each graph.
